728981f-a.title: Richmond: Hylan Boulevard - Ainsworth Avenue
728981f-a.text:
3588 Hylan Boulevard, south side, at Ainsworth Avenue. The
maps of u874, 1BB7, and 1898 show it to have been part of the J. J.
Crooke estate. It Aas later (907 map) on the property of the Willet
Realty Co., and still later (1917 map) on the Willard Realty Co.
property. It is now (1938) within Staten Island Marine Park.
May 14, 1932.
P. L. Sperr
